snippet.title: When GRAVITY kicks in - FUNNIEST bloopers of poor powerless KIDS!
snippet.description:
Well, everybody once faced the Newton's laws for first time. For some of these kidos, it was a bit painful, but these fails and falls are priceless, aren't they! :D Hope you like our video mix, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
